			"index": 1,
			"condition": "",
			"prompt": "${loopMember}. <break size='0.5'/> <anim name='Greetings_01'>You know, you're one of my favorite people in the world named ${loopMember}</anim>. <anim name='Affection_01' nonBlocking='true' /> <ssa cat='affection'/>",
